{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","text":"MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The map view that requested the annotation view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The object representing the annotation that is about to be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The view object to display for the given annotation or ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to display an annotation image instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample"]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Implement this method to mark a point annotation with a view object. If you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method or have it return ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" for that annotation, then implement","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"annotation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is an instance of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" (or equal to the map view’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property), return an instance of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(or a subclass thereof).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading","level":4,"text":"Related examples"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images, learn how to specify what","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to use for a given ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object on your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:viewForAnnotation:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L753","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapViewDelegate"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"View representing an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" on screen.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnnotationViewExample":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","title":"Custom Annotation View","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/annotationviewexample","role":"article","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add a custom annotation view"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property of the map view displayed in your application.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNUserLocation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:viewForAnnotation:":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:","title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"}}}